%% Box Ledger — Box Hierarchy
%% Global Ledger -> File Directory Ledger -> Box Ledger -> per-class BOX.md instances.

flowchart TD
    GL["Global Ledger<br/>LEDGERS/GLOBAL_LEDGER.md"]:::project
    FDL["File Directory Ledger<br/>(maps what directories exist)"]:::project
    BL["Box Ledger<br/>LEDGERS/BOX_LEDGER.md<br/>(defines what a Box IS)"]:::self
    Template["BOX_LEDGER_TEMPLATE.md<br/>(the stamp)"]:::template
    DirTemplate["DIRECTORY_ORIENTATION_TEMPLATE.md<br/>(lighter alternative)"]:::template

    GL --> FDL
    FDL --> BL
    BL --> Template
    BL --> DirTemplate

    %% First-wave Boxes (Section 10)
    Template --> LEDGERSBox["LEDGERS/BOX.md<br/>(class: ledger)"]:::firstwave
    Template --> ClientBoxesBox["Auto/Client Boxes/BOX.md<br/>(class: client)"]:::firstwave
    Template --> OrchBox["Auto/orchestrator/BOX.md<br/>(class: orchestrator)"]:::firstwave
    Template --> InboxBox["Auto/comeketo-inbox/BOX.md<br/>(class: inbox-skill)"]:::firstwave
    Template --> BedrockBox["CCAgentindex/BOX.md<br/>(class: bedrock)"]:::firstwave
    Template --> AppUIBox["project root BOX.md<br/>(class: app-ui)"]:::firstwave

    %% Per-class instances (third wave for clients)
    ClientBoxesBox --> Brenda["Brenda & Steve/BOX.md<br/>(third wave)"]:::thirdwave
    ClientBoxesBox --> Hugo["Hugo Casillas/BOX.md<br/>(third wave)"]:::thirdwave
    ClientBoxesBox --> Others["...26 other Client Boxes<br/>(audit markers only for now)"]:::client

    %% Second wave
    Template --> StaffBox["Auto/Staff Boxes/BOX.md<br/>(second wave)"]:::secondwave
    Template --> OnboardBox["Auto/Onboard Scripts/BOX.md<br/>(second wave)"]:::secondwave
    Template --> SubagentBox["Subagent Boxes/BOX.md<br/>(second wave)"]:::secondwave
    Template --> DraftsBox["Ledger Drafts/BOX.md<br/>(second wave)"]:::secondwave

    %% Triad spine reference
    Triad["DEC-2026-04-29-001<br/>Triad Spine:<br/>Box + Ledger + Sub-agent"]:::decision
    Triad -.->|operationalizes the<br/>Box leg via| BL

